This asset is situated within the tightly held Monash Industrial Precinct, and provides a rare leasing opportunity for occupiers wanting to be in this area.

The property provides excellent functionality and access to surrounding arteials. The demand for this industrial region is reflected by surrounding occupiers which include Pfizer, Mercedez Benz Australia, Crown Forklifts, Couriers Please and Capital Smart.
